{"id": 455, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都穿啥去运动？", "description": "当我穿上我的老头汗衫，那就是我要去运动了……", "record_count": 2322, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606004902W9IKxY84SyFiCPXv.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-03T12:15:31Z", "options": [{"id": 8192, "content": "短袖+GUP裤子+OLLO鞋子", "image": "img/option/option/201606042348574etBxJ0HurnflGpk.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161213}, {"id": 7690, "content": "最便宜的文化衫和旧的运动裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156652}, {"id": 18703, "content": "安全套", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 7443, "content": "鞋最重要。衣服可以稍微凑合着。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156251}, {"id": 6424, "content": "穿旧的或者过时的T恤短裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 354, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6425, "content": "专业的鞋，鞋一定要是专业的", "image": null, "praise_count": 613, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7449, "content": "穿一双舒服的鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156305}, {"id": 6426, "content": "具有特殊功能比如排汗、防水的衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 247, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 6428, "content": "形成整体造型的运动装备", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7462, "content": "穿舒适的鞋子，纯色的运动衣，带一条超吸汗的毛巾。感觉自己活力满满的，运动就是一种享受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156368}, {"id": 7207, "content": "必须有一双舒适的跑鞋+透气短裤，其他随意啦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 81582}, {"id": 6955, "content": "明星同款我会说？", "image": "img/option/option/2016060423492635TdcCHEp8jnWo76.jpg", "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3797}, {"id": 6956, "content": "穿舒适，看起来比较干净的衣服。面料的选择，还有专业的运动鞋。这些都是最基本的要求。", "image": "img/option/option/20160606000656LVGJTYXE6ACxoef5.jpg", "praise_count": 253, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153641}, {"id": 6957, "content": "水平是次要的，装备一定要专业", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 6958, "content": "鞋子一定要专业，但是衣服可以迪卡侬～科科", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142518}, {"id": 8494, "content": "嗯…我有两双跑鞋，不同牌子…换着穿的时候…袜子要必须要和脚上穿得鞋是同一个牌子的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164346}, {"id": 6960, "content": "祖传人字拖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134885}, {"id": 6961, "content": "紧身衣………一定要紧！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 10861}, {"id": 6962, "content": "看运动类型，篮球就篮球衫裤篮球鞋，跑步就排汗tee和跑鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96447}, {"id": 6963, "content": "之前穿过准备洗的", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146756}, {"id": 6964, "content": "穿的倍儿有运动范~休闲t，紧身运动裤，美美的慢跑鞋，计步器，就是跑了两圈就跪了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152364}, {"id": 6970, "content": "老头衫+花裤衩+随便什么运动鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688}, {"id": 6971, "content": "买了设计师限量款还有别的机会显摆吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 6972, "content": "看起来不太怂运动起来又很舒服的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141422}, {"id": 6973, "content": "一双合脚的鞋子+一颗想跑的心……穿不穿无所谓了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 164, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103310}, {"id": 6974, "content": "必须是耐克，，。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 50612}, {"id": 6976, "content": "这项运动领域的领先品牌，无论是衣服，还是鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151537}, {"id": 6978, "content": "随便\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141795}, {"id": 6979, "content": "汗衫＋短裤＋板鞋＋电子表", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142461}, {"id": 6980, "content": "可以不穿吗", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211108tJnVhRsoYP3cEIOD.jpg", "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109839}, {"id": 6981, "content": "必须是紧身速干衣 因为他穿起来很酷", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234903VvaUQy9NH6ksWmcG.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 93406}, {"id": 6982, "content": "快干运动衣（包括球衣），这样当天晚上回来洗洗，第二天要去运动还可以继续穿~", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129850}, {"id": 6985, "content": "鞋子一定要是跑鞋，亚瑟士 美津浓等专业款\r\n衣服嘛。。。。舒服就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116463}, {"id": 6986, "content": "鞋子舒适自由最重要，衣服穿吸汗的材料，随身听必备，运动手表必备", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151625}, {"id": 6987, "content": "裸奔才是王道", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 65889}, {"id": 6988, "content": "热裤和酷炫的运动鞋?穿美美的才有动力减肥啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153786}, {"id": 14927, "content": "一颗热爱运动的心！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228578}, {"id": 6998, "content": "飞跃、飞跃、飞跃…!", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55104}, {"id": 7001, "content": "耐克T恤短裤和跑鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148294}, {"id": 7002, "content": "热裤加跑鞋?穿美美哒才有动力减肥！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153786}, {"id": 7003, "content": "一定要很舒服，时尚，低调", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117090}, {"id": 7004, "content": "坚决不穿阿迪耐克，亚瑟士索康尼亚瑟士还不错～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145769}, {"id": 7006, "content": "球服或者宽松的衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153851}, {"id": 9310, "content": "You have the monopoly on useful ina-'mftionoarenrt monopolies illegal? ;)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7014, "content": "在衣柜抓到什么就是什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153198}, {"id": 7017, "content": "此", "image": "img/option/option/201606042348490f3XvrKai1PUgmoe.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153894}, {"id": 14186, "content": "跑鞋和袜子。不穿运动鞋不穿袜子。不运动。因为平时不穿袜子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 211969}, {"id": 7020, "content": "永远的道服以及各种道服。（ 你说的运动，又没说跑步 ）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138098}, {"id": 7277, "content": "亚瑟士的鞋。安德玛的紧身衣。 没双好鞋跑步伤害太大  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155209}, {"id": 7023, "content": "??", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234858pxaMBW78H2bNyJzw.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103970}]}